description: This isn't your everyday comfort food, Barroluco Argentine Comfort Food is serving up something special for you.This is a mobile restaurant 45 years in the making, and bringing the proud culinary traditions of its homeland to the streets of Columbus. Soon to be the city's first fast-casual Argentine eatery on 4 wheels, this food truck is bringing a rustic feel with modern flair to your next meal. For Barroluco, it's all about good food, good attitude, and a great community. If that sounds like what you're looking for, then this is definitely the food truck you've been waiting for!
name: Barroluco Argentine Comfort Food
